OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUS journalist Terry        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FAnderson dies aged 76      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, US journalist Terry Anderson, who was  
OL,6, held hostage for nearly seven years    
OL,7, during Lebanon's civil war, has died   
OL,8, aged 76.                               
OL,10,FAnderson was the chief Middle East     
OL,11,Fcorrespondent for the Associated Press 
OL,12,Fwhen he was captured by Islamist       
OL,13,Fmilitants in 1985 during what became   
OL,14,Fknown as the Lebanon hostage crisis.   
OL,16,FHe died at his home in Greenwood Lake, 
OL,17,FNew York, on Sunday, his daughter said.
OL,19,FSulome Anderson said he had found peace
OL,20,Fin recent years after the ordeal.      
